<div class="gallerytext">
</div>
</div></li>
<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px"><div style="width: 155px">
<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px;"><div style="margin:30px auto;"><a href="/File:Orange_Pi_One_IR_schema.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Orange Pi One IR schema.jpg" src="/images/thumb/2/28/Orange_Pi_One_IR_schema.jpg/120px-Orange_Pi_One_IR_schema.jpg" width="120" height="90"/></a></div></div>
<div class="gallerytext">
</div>
</div></li>
</ul>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Orange_Pi_Lite"> Orange Pi Lite </span></h2>
<p>Please note that the boards are sold without any heatsink. This is just the <a href="/User:Tkaiser#Sunxi_devices_lying_around:" title="User:Tkaiser">tester's standard heatsink for all H3 boards</a> now.
</p>
<ul class="gallery">
<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px"><div style="width: 155px">
